checking the version at each call is not the best practice. You should put a condition on the declaration of the function at module level:

``` python
if LooseVersion(nibabel.__version__) > LooseVersion('2.0.0'):
    def get_affine(img):
        return img.affine
else:
    def get_affine(img):
        return img.get_affine()
```
